modName: The Witcher Font Replacer Standalone - Skyrim - By Setvi
summary:
TWFRS will add a Witcher font replacer, Morpheus, as a standalone one, for Skyrim.
The .RAR file come into .ESP and BSA version for an easy test/install/uninstall purpose.
It's not a port from Valistar, it's my own version done as a .ESP/BSA files.
